title: 9 Different Eyeliner Looks
description:
How to apply eyeliner? How to slay your winged eyeliner? I show you guys how to create 9 different eyeliner looks. From everyday simple eyeliner to dramatic eyeliner looks. I share all of my tips and tricks on how to finally master the art of eyeliner and how to apply eyeliner using gel eyeliner. I hope you guys enjoy this tutorial and find it helpful. My personal favorite is the "feline" look. What's your go-to style?

As always, thank you guys for everything and I hope you all have a beautiful day today!
Remember: You're beautiful. Always think positive. Things happen for a reason.

LOVE YOU ALL!

XOXO Lupe
